<p>Engagement Velocity measures how actively customers interact with your business profile. AI Mode treats engagement as a real-time popularity signal.</p>
<p>The March 2026 update shifted Google's algorithm from "prominence" (domain authority, backlink volume) to "popularity" (real-world engagement metrics). A new business with high engagement can now outrank an established brand with stronger domain authority.</p>
