<h3>Post Structure for AI</h3>
<p>AI systems parse Google Posts for keywords, sentiment, and recency. Structure your posts to maximize what AI can extract.</p>
<p><strong>Optimal post structure:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Opening sentence:</strong> Include your primary service and location</li>
