<p>AI extracts: downtown Austin dental, same-day Invisalign consultations, 3D scanning, teeth whitening kit, phone number, online booking.</p>
<h3>The Decay Rate</h3>
<p>AI Mode prioritizes fresh data. A GBP post older than 7 days carries significantly less weight than a post published today. This is what AgencyJet calls the "decay rate" — visibility drops measurably after 30 days of inactivity.</p>
<p><strong>What this means:</strong>
- One post per month is not enough
- Weekly posting is the minimum for competitive markets
- Daily posting is optimal but requires automation</p>
